<%
  meta property: {
    robots: "nofollow",
    charset: "utf-8",
    google: "notranslate",
    alexaVerifyID: "xDHxdz_2gqDx5OsChw00vOyCk3k"
  }
%>

<%
  meta title: "Community Guidelines",
     description: "Learn how to make most out of the hungryhead - a new way to start entrepreneurship for students studying in schools, colleges and universities",
     keywords: %w(student\ entrepreneurship school\ entrepreneurs student\ entrepreneurs idea\ collaboration universities\ entrepreneurship collaborative\ network\ students schools\ entrepreneurship entrepreneurship\ ideas idea\ validation student\ idea\ validation student\ idea\ collaboration global\ ideas\ platform)
%>

<% cache(['beta', 'community_guidelines', 'v1']) do %>
<div class="learn-wrapper bg-white">
  <div class="learn">
    <div class="jumbotron no-margin" data-pages="parallax">
        <div class="rules-photo inner">
        <div class="container vmiddle">
        <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-8 auto-margin text-center">
                  <div class="hero-section z-index-10">
                      <h1 class="text-white bold">
                        Community guidelines
                      </h1>
                      <p class="text-white no-margin fs-16">
                        Make the most out of hungryhead
                      </p>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="story">
    <div class="wrapper-small">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-10 auto-margin">
        <p class="fs-16 semi-bold">
          <strong>Hungryhead is an online community</strong> to validate and build new student startup ideas. We founded hungryhead on a few core values –– <strong>trust, respect and openness</strong>. It’s all up to us to ensure hungryhead is a safe and open platform to share and validate new student startup ideas.
        </p>
        <h5 class="bold">
          We are pointing out a few guidelines that we hope you would keep in mind along the way!
        </h5>
        <div class="divider b-b b-green b-md b-small m-t-20"></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="semi-bold m-t-30">
            <i class="fa fa-times text-danger"></i> Don't SPAM
          </h3>
          <p class="fs-16">
            This includes link-bombing, colluding on an idea, promoting third-party services, and posting irrelevant or personal content. The comment, feedback and messaging system are here so that everyone can easily communicate, ask questions and provide feedbacks. Please don't use it for SPAMMING others.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="semi-bold m-t-30">
              <i class="fa fa-check text-green"></i> Trust and Respect
            </h3>
            <p class="fs-16">
              Collaboration is really important for hungryhead and therefore, to have meaningful collaboration it's integral to have respect for each others ideas. Don’t post obscene, personal, hateful, or objectionable content. If you don't like someone else idea please, try to communicate your thoughts respectfully.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="semi-bold m-t-30">
              <i class="fa fa-check text-green"></i> Share
            </h3>
            <p class="fs-16">
              The idea is a product of our thought and therefore, the more it's shared the bigger it becomes. If you see an idea that you feel would be interesting please vote, feedback and share. The community is a place where nothing gets unnoticed if you contribute it will return back to you.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="divider b-b b-green b-md b-small m-t-20"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-master-lightest full-border-light text-center wrapper-small full-border-light-bottom no-overflow p-b-100" id="intro">
    <div class="col-sm-8 col-md-8 auto-margin">
      <h1 class="m-t-5 m-b-20">
        To get started
      </h1>
      <%= link_to('Click here', get_started_path, class: 'main-button m-t-10 fs-13 bold') %>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
<% end %>
<%= render partial: 'globals/footer' %>

